  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user\r\nI want to be able to delete a chat\r\nSo I don't get distracted by it\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nWe changed the behaviour of the *Delete chat* option in the chat menu:\r\n\r\nFor all the chats this will:\r\n\r\n- Remove all previous messages\r\n- Older messages will not appear again\r\n- The chat should not be visibile in the home screen\r\n\r\nIn addition to this, some behaviour is chat specific:\r\n\r\nIn a 1 to 1 chat:\r\n\r\n- If a new message from the contact is received, the chat will appear again in the home screen\r\n\r\nIn a group chat:\r\n\r\n- The user should also leave the group, and will not receive any message until he is invited again\r\n\r\nIn scope of this we should also remove the *Leave chat* option from public chats & group chats.\r\n",
